item.description:
Join us for Stump Team Trivia at Canyon Cafe in Westborough. Located on Rt. 9 westbound, this restaurant/bar has good food and is conveniently located. Stump team trivia is always lots of fun- so join us for a fun night with friendly people and good food.

We will meet at 7:30. Trivia starts at 8pm. If you have trouble finding us, please call Catherine at 774 232 0000. Everyone pays for their own food/drinks.
item.how_to_find_us: Look for Catherine (see photo) inside. If need to, please call 774 232 0000
item.name: Stump Team Trivia at Canyon Cafe, Westborough
